{"tid":2165474,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"資訊科技相關職位加薪再嬴大市　JobsDB 整合過往五年薪酬數據反映IT人才渴市","createTime":"2020-08-20T00:19:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T08:42:42.000Z","uid":85524,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a7350368409afa0985ff467938081c215c3fdff7","tid":2165474,"uid":85524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T00:19:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.jobsdb.com/en-hk/shorten/?p=50112\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.jobsdb.com%2Fen-hk%2Fshorten%2F%3Fp%3D50112&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufVEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=14aff12c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.jobsdb.com/en-hk/shorten/?p=50112</a><br />\n<br />\nIT又win <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nIT 行業薪酬加幅大幅拋離整體數字<br />\n全球經濟不穩定因素及各項抗疫措施令多個行業、工種面臨重大挑戰，今年獲得加人工的本地打工仔只有 50%，比往年減少兩成，加薪幅度亦大幅下調至只有 1.3%，部分行業如旅遊、零售更錄得超過 8%負增長，資訊科技工種卻突圍而出，高於平均數有 66% 從業員獲得加薪，平均升幅更高達 6.1%，亦獲派較大份花紅（1.8個月）。事實上，過往五年來 IT 工種人工增幅均跑贏大市，今年對比尤其突出。<br />\n<br />\n開發人員最吃香　升幅拋離大市十倍<br />\nJobsDB 網站今年薪酬報告專頁公布各個工種獲加薪最多的職位排名。在 IT 工種之中，開發人員（Developer）的人工增幅最高達 13.9%，其次為高級分析程式員（Senior Analyst Programmer），獲得 9.5% 升幅，與及程式編寫員（Programmer）亦獲 9% 升幅。<br />\n<br />\nJobsDB 香港區行政總裁仇崑石先生表示：「與資訊科技和數碼轉型有關的產業發展仍然蓬勃，這是由於各行各業都需要科技支援及數碼轉型，以簡化工作流程，改善效率，從而為企業迎來新的經營模式。另外，香港在 <span class=\"red\">eCommerce （電子商務）</span>、Mobile（流動裝置相關項目）、AI（人工智能）、Cloud（雲端）等領域上仍然缺人，而支援數碼轉型的數據分析亦十分渴才，由此造就相關行業的人工增長。」"},{"pid":"cfa27fcc8764dd0f72d30f284322c8934b696891","tid":2165474,"uid":228955,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T00:24:37.000Z","msg":"加人工 都因為之前底"},{"pid":"8a92f88c640d5b6b6b2023ebd253806d09bfa513","tid":2165474,"uid":236356,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"cfa27fcc8764dd0f72d30f284322c8934b696891","tid":2165474,"uid":228955,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T00:24:37.000Z","msg":"加人工 都因為之前底"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T00:26:07.000Z","msg":"10k-&gt;11k<br />\n加幅達10%，大幅跑贏通脹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c77098f9a459870958df5f9042dd64a6ff3f608","tid":2165474,"uid":246133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T00:27:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加人工 都因為之前<span class=\"red\">低</span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b9902bbdbb72d1e8f7e54c59d0e5774f4f77cdf1","tid":2165474,"uid":57532,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T00:32:05.000Z","msg":"因為有咩事第一批炒IT狗先咪多空缺，<br />\n然後極低薪請新人，年年加10%，<br />\n加到咁上下又再炒曬。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67c38863e9718232942f17ce5e1f7d82899ee0d6","tid":2165474,"uid":102700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T00:32:27.000Z","msg":"公司d it個個60K up<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac153f5edcec85330706faa627b95553fd3b62ec","tid":2165474,"uid":13901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b9902bbdbb72d1e8f7e54c59d0e5774f4f77cdf1","tid":2165474,"uid":57532,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T00:32:05.000Z","msg":"因為有咩事第一批炒IT狗先咪多空缺，<br />\n然後極低薪請新人，年年加10%，<br />\n加到咁上下又再炒曬。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T00:33:55.000Z","msg":"學識係source code留屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d49763333e6c733f75233f037299330049d8e8","tid":2165474,"uid":184103,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T00:35:31.000Z","msg":"連登仔: 假既 唔信 IT係狗係垃圾"},{"pid":"e80b0aa617af36d6b248b4f67475fbef55df779e","tid":2165474,"uid":48077,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T00:38:26.000Z","msg":"又水一班人入行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50b7df61b5e19ba73e344baa888a73d38d81b8ed","tid":2165474,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T00:45:53.000Z","msg":"裁員 <br />\n被迫以較低人工